replies.author: xinyang0326
replies.txt_content: 卡区块报错 实体名:ttinkerer:infusedGrainBlock(3289) chunk:-2,-5 计算得出相关文件：r.-1.-1.mca[30.27] 推荐使用NBTexplorer无损修复~

replies.author: luckyyong
replies.txt_content:
Block type: ID #3289 (tile.infusedGrainBlock // thaumic.tinkerer.common.block.BlockInfusedGrain)
        Block data value: 7 / 0x7 / 0b0111
        Block location: World: (-17,65,-71), Chunk: (at 15,4,9 in -2,-5; contains blocks -32,0,-80 to -17,255,-65), Region: (-1,-1; contains chunks -32,-32 to -1,-1, blocks -512,0,-512 to -1,255,-1)
如上，(-17,65,-71)这个位置有一个id为3289的方块导致了崩溃，可以尝试到world/region中删除r.-1.-1这个区块的地图解决问题

replies.author: luckyyong
replies.txt_content: 不过需要注意的是删除了上述文件以后会把512x512区域的地图重置
